Phase 4 — VPN:
	Branch: phase/4-vpn
	Architecture: Network Extension framework (NEVPNManager/NETunnelProviderManager) — replaces CLI-based approach
	Rework Tasks (replaces original CLI/helper implementation):
	- Delete CLI/helper infrastructure: VPNDefinition.swift, ProcessCommandExecutor.swift, VPNCommandExecuting.swift, HelperConstants.swift, PrivilegedHelperManager.swift, PrivilegedHelper/ target, MockVPNCommandExecutor.swift
	- Remove PrivilegedHelper target from project.yml
	- Implement VPNConfigurationProviding protocol — abstraction over NETunnelProviderManager for testability
	- Rewrite VPNManager — auto-discover system VPN profiles via NETunnelProviderManager.loadAllFromPreferences()
	- Implement real-time VPN status monitoring via NEVPNStatusDidChange notification (replace 10s polling)
	- Implement VPN configuration change detection via NEVPNConfigurationChange notification
	- Implement VPN connect/disconnect via NEVPNConnection.startVPNTunnel() / stopVPNTunnel()
	- Implement VPN provider icon mapping via NETunnelProviderProtocol.providerBundleIdentifier
	- Simplify VPNState — wrap NEVPNManager with displayName, status, isEnabled, provider icon
	- Gate VPN features behind LicenseManager.isPaid
	- Update VPNSectionView — remove CLI warnings, add provider icons, status dot colors for all NEVPNStatus states
	- Update VPNSettingsView — remove "Request a VPN" button, simplify to show/hide toggles + multi-VPN warning toggle
	- Update SettingsStore — use localizedDescription as VPN identifier for enabledVPNs persistence
	- Wire IPService auto-refresh to VPN state changes (via NEVPNStatusDidChange)
	- Update AppDelegate — replace CLI-based VPN wiring with Network Extension setup
	- Add NetworkExtension framework to project.yml
	- Try without com.apple.developer.networking.vpn.api entitlement first (app is unsandboxed)
	- Write unit tests for VPNManager (discovery, status mapping, connect/disconnect, enabled filtering, multi-VPN warning)
	- Implement MockVPNConfigurationProvider for tests
	- Add VoiceOver accessibility labels to all Phase 4 UI elements
	- All user-facing strings use String(localized:)
	- Update CLAUDE.md tree with file changes
	- Manual test against PRD user stories 16-19 (VPN management — story 20 obsolete)
	- Manual test against PRD user stories 45, 48 (VPN configuration — stories 46, 47, 47a obsolete)
	- Manual test: VPN state change triggers external IP refresh
	- Scott tests with real WireGuard, Tailscale setup (Scott) @tags(scott)
	- Regression test: all Phase 1-3 user stories

